4001). In support of sUSV
NEXT, DIU will use Other Transaction (OT) authority (10 U.S.C. 4022) and executes a structured solicitation and competitive down-select process via Commercial
Solutions Opening (CSO). Prototype OT awards planned for APR 2024; minimum viable product The sUSV contract, to support the timeline needed to scale up
production to support the needs of the
operational commanders.

