       (Shipbuilding) of the Reconciliation Exhibit.

       "The FY 2026 request was reduced by 0.230 million for Advisory and Assistance Services to promote efficiencies and advance the policies of the Administration
       in alignment with Executive Order 14222, "Implementing the President's Department of Government Efficiency Cost Efficiency Initiative."

       FY 2026 increase of $7.267M addresses critical cyber vulnerabilities and increases cyber survivability efforts of LCAC C4N systems.




