FY 2025 funding supports engineering development and design of End of Life (EOL) hardware and software
replacements, enhanced technology performance including M-code capable Global Position System (GPS)
receivers (Embedded GPS / Inertial Navigation System (EGI)) and Dismounted Assured Positioning Navigation
and Timing System (DAPS), Operating System updates, and critical cyber survivability enhancements.
Funds will support development of Technical Data Package (TDP) for Integrated Vibration, Balance and
Health Management System (IVB-HEMS) interim solution, Integrated Condition Assessment System (ICAS)
replacement and integration of modernized transmission algorithms of tactical radios. Funding will also support
the completion of Initial Operational Test and Evaluation (IOT&E).
