the lines of operational mission needs. This update focuses on the operational characteristics of Tasking,
Collection, Processing, Exploitation, and Dissemination (TCPED) of METOC data and information. Identified
efforts supporting METOC are realigned to projects and activities that align to the TCPED updated program
