                                                                                                                     FY 2024    FY 2025      Base        OOC        Total

• Seek to improve the ease and effectiveness of wargame execution by developing new WIE visualizations and
user/ participant interfaces in the FY25 HAF "Title 10” wargame series comprised of Futures Game 25 (FG 25)
and Global Engagement 25 (GE 25)—where FG is a high-classification deep-dive into capabilities 15-20 years
out and GE is an Ally-informed look at military theater competition between now and that period.

There are no OCO funds programmed or executed in this PE
