Increase corrects inadvertent reduction to baseline at Agency level which reduced the ability to meet CSAF
increased posture for advanced Title 10 wargaming across the Air Force Enterprise. Reestablishes baseline
from previous approved POM submissions by reconnecting requirements with normal inflation increases.
